- Respect all allergies (non-negotiable): {{ JSON.stringify($json.family_profile.allergies) }}
- Avoid dislikes: {{ JSON.stringify($json.family_profile.dislikes) }}
- At most one candidate per primary protein across the {{ $json.num_proposals }}
- Leanna is focused on weight loss — prefer high-protein, macro-friendly options
- Serves 3+ (leftovers welcome)

CRITICAL: Choose recipes whose ingredient lists OVERLAP meaningfully — the family will pick {{ $json.target_approvals }} and wants a small grocery bill.

For each selected recipe return the exact spoonacular_id integer (from the [ID:...] tag), a short family-friendly description, and the key ingredients you'll use for overlap scoring.

